name [Krunal Dodiya]
organization unit [KD]
organization [QuizMonstr]
city [Ahmedabad]
state [Gujarat]
country [IN]

alias quizmonstr
password quizmonstr@1987
appId com.quizmonstr

1) generate keystore
------------
keytool -genkey -v -keystore quizmonstr.keystore -alias quizmonstr -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000

2) Place the quizmonstr.keystore file under the android/app directory in your project folder.

3) Edit the file ~/.gradle/gradle.properties or android/gradle.properties, and add the following (replace ***** with the correct keystore password, alias and key password),
-------
MYAPP_RELEASE_STORE_FILE=quizmonstr.keystore
MYAPP_RELEASE_KEY_ALIAS=quizmonstr
MYAPP_RELEASE_STORE_PASSWORD=quizmonstr@1987
MYAPP_RELEASE_KEY_PASSWORD=quizmonstr@1987

Edit the file android/app/build.gradle in your project folder, and add the signing config,
------------
android {
    ...
    defaultConfig { ... }
    signingConfigs {
        release {
            if (project.hasProperty('MYAPP_RELEASE_STORE_FILE')) {
                storeFile file(MYAPP_RELEASE_STORE_FILE)
                storePassword MYAPP_RELEASE_STORE_PASSWORD
                keyAlias MYAPP_RELEASE_KEY_ALIAS
                keyPassword MYAPP_RELEASE_KEY_PASSWORD
            }
        }
    }
    buildTypes {
        release {
            ...
            signingConfig signingConfigs.release
        }
    }
}

$ cd android
$ ./gradlew assembleRelease